 <name>ssd1306</name>
 <channel>pecl.php.net</channel>
 <summary>PHP extension for SSD1306 OLED displays</summary>
 <description>
  This extension provides PHP bindings for controlling SSD1306 OLED displays via I2C.
  It offers a comprehensive API for display initialization, pixel manipulation, graphics
  drawing, text rendering, and scrolling effects. Compatible with 128x64, 128x32, and
  96x16 display sizes commonly used in embedded projects.
  
  Features:
  - I2C communication with SSD1306 displays
  - Pixel-level drawing operations
  - Graphics primitives (lines, rectangles, circles)
  - Text rendering with scalable fonts
  - Display scrolling effects
  - Multiple display size support
  - Hardware abstraction for easy integration
 </description>
