  Features:
  - Complete SSD1306 display support
  - I2C communication
  - Graphics and text rendering
  - Scrolling effects
  - Multiple display sizes
  - Comprehensive API documentation
  
  Requirements:
  - PHP 7.4+ or PHP 8.x
  - Linux with I2C support
  - i2c-tools and libi2c-dev packages
 </notes>
